message: Hi Bob, I'm offering this product for sale at a price of $12,000. I believe it offers significant value at this price point. What do you think?
Hello Alice, thank you for the offer. I understand the value of the product, but I am only willing to pay up to $9,500. I hope we can come to an agreement.
Hi Bob, thanks for the offer. I appreciate your interest, but $9,500 is a bit too low for me.  Would you be willing to meet in the middle at $11,000?
Hello Alice, I appreciate your response. I am still not able to meet at $11,000. I would like to propose $10,000 as my maximum offer.
